.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-6::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, house, punk, reggae
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: handball, basketball, rugby, skiing
1. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
2. the fan of reggae is the person who's sport is rugby##1
3. the fan of reggae is on the far right##1
4. the fan of house is the person who's sport is handball##1
5. the fan of punk is between the fan of gospel and the fan of house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| Music-Genre   | house     | punk           | gospel | reggae  |
| Sport         | handball | skiing | basketball   | rugby |

