.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-7::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: dubstep, r&b, classical, funk
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, scooter, boat, bike
1. the fan of r&b is the person driving the train##1
2. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person driving the train##1
3. the person driving the bike is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1
4. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
5. the fan of dubstep is between the person driving the train and the fan of classical##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | funk   | r&b | dubstep | classical      |
| Transport     | boat | train    | scooter  | bike |

