.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-9::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  chef, teacher, doctor, engineer
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, trike, taxi, helicopter
1. the doctor is between the person driving the jet-ski and the chef##2
2. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the chef##1
3. the engineer is on the right of the chef##1
4. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
5. the chef is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |      4       |
| Job         | teacher | doctor | chef | engineer |
| Transport   | jet-ski         | helicopter       | trike    | taxi         |

