.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-10::.
There 4 different types of food: grapefruit, onion, cherry, radish
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: soccer, rugby, cycling, skateboarding
1. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person eating radish##1
2. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person eating cherry##1
3. the person eating grapefruit is on the right of the person eating onion##1
4. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
5. the person who's sport is rugby is between the person eating onion and the person who's sport is skateboarding##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Food    | radish   | cherry      | onion   | grapefruit  |
| Sport   | skateboarding | rugby | cycling | soccer |

