.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-11::.
There 4 different types of food: potato, cucumber, strawberry, pineapple
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: spy, musical, mystery, action
1. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
2. the person eating cucumber is between the person eating pineapple and the person eating potato##2
3. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
4. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person eating potato##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |      4      |
| Food          | potato     | cucumber | pineapple   | strawberry        |
| Movie-Genre   | spy | mystery   | musical | action |

