.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-12::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, cooking, photography, dancing
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, funk, salsa, ambient
1. the fan of salsa is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
2. the fan of funk is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
3. the fan of metal is the person who's hobby is gardening##1
4. the person who's hobby is photography is the fan of funk##1
5. the fan of metal is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
6. the fan of funk is between the person who's hobby is cooking and the person who's hobby is dancing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby         | cooking | photography | dancing | gardening |
| Music-Genre   | salsa          | funk     | ambient  | metal     |

