4. the accountant is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2        |    3     |     4     |
| Job           | accountant | firefighter | pilot | coach     |
| Movie-Genre   | epic   | scientific    | time-travel   | superhero |

