3. the owner of the dog is between the owner of the frog and the dutch##2
4. the owner of the hamster is the owner of the hamster##1
5. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the owner of the snake##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| Nationality   | polish | dutch | american | argentine |
| Pet           | snake  | hamster  | dog | frog      |

