2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
3. the egyptian is the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
4. the person who's sport is lacrosse is between the german and the indian##2
5. the indian is the person who's sport is badminton##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Nationality   | egyptian   | german   | canadian | indian |
| Sport         | snowboarding | tennis | lacrosse     | badminton    |

