.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-20::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, puzzles, video-games, gardening
4 different pets are kept: bird, hedgehog, fish, rat
1. the owner of the hedgehog is on the far left##1
2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is between the owner of the bird and the person who's hobby is gardening##2
3. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
4. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the far right##1
5. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the owner of the fish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby   | video-games    | gardening     | rock-climbing | puzzles |
| Pet     | hedgehog | rat | fish       | bird     |

 